OL,3,CReform leader of Warwickshire County
OL,4,CCouncil bans flags ahead of Christmas
OL,6,FThe Reform leader of Warwickshire
OL,7,FCounty Council has banned flags on
OL,8,Flampposts ahead of Christmas due to
OL,9,F"health and safety issues".
OL,11,FIn a statement posted on X, Councillor
OL,12,FGeorge Finch said he is "immensely
OL,13,Fproud of our national flags" but that
OL,14,Fthey are not practical alongside
OL,15,FChristmas lights.
OL,17,FMr Finch said flags wrapped around
OL,18,Flampposts in "wet and windy conditions
OL,19,Fand potentially coming into contact
OL,20,Fwith lights" creates a "fire risk".
