OL,6,FIn July, Councillor George Finch, who
OL,7,Fis 19, became the youngest council
OL,8,Fleader in the UK.
OL,10,FOne of his priorities was a new flag
OL,11,Fpolicy - limiting council flag-flying
OL,12,Fto the Union, St George's and
OL,13,FWarwickshire flags.
OL,15,FIn August, he told ITV News Central
OL,16,Fabout his views on the flag policy at
OL,17,FWarwickshire County Council and the
OL,18,FLGBTQ+ flag.
