OL,6,FHe said: "It wasn't just about the
OL,7,Fflag. No. You know, I do believe that
OL,8,Fpolitical flags with political symbols
OL,9,Fdon't represent the vast majority of
OL,10,FWarwickshire.
OL,12,F"Yes. We have people in the LGBT
OL,13,Fcommunity. Fine. Equal. They are
OL,14,Fnormal people. But they don't need a
OL,15,Fflag.
OL,17,F"You know, you haven't got a flag for
OL,18,Fmen's mental health. You haven't got a
OL,19,Fflag about children SEND needs.
