OL,6,F"So why do they get a flag? It should
OL,7,Fbe a non-political thing. It should be
OL,8,Fa Union flag, the Saint George's flag
OL,9,Fand the Warwickshire flag. And then if
OL,10,Fthere's a royal attendance, then we
OL,11,Fraise the Royal Standard, that's it.
OL,13,F"It's simple. It's not a political
OL,14,Fdecision."
